@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token =

### ================== ASIGNACIÓN ROL-RECURSO ==================

### Obtener todas las asignaciones rol-recurso
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear una asignación rol-recurso
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource_id": 1,
  "role_id": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Obtener asignación rol-recurso por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar una asignación rol-recurso
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource_id": 2,
  "role_id": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Eliminar una asignación físicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar una asignación lógicamente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resource-roles/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
